---
import { loadProfile, loadInterests } from "../../lib/content/loader";

const profile = loadProfile();
const interests = loadInterests();
---

<section id="about" class="py-16 md:py-24 scroll-mt-20">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-16" data-animate>
      <h2 class="section-heading">About <span class="neon-text">Me</span></h2>
      <p class="section-subheading">Engineer, builder, founder</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-12 items-start" data-animate>
      <!-- Headshot -->
      <div class="md:col-span-1 flex justify-center">
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="w-56 h-72 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden headshot-frame">
            <img
              src="/img/graduation.jpg"
              alt="Caide Spriestersbach — UCT Graduation"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover headshot-img"
              style="object-position: 50% 12%; transform: scale(1.5);"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="absolute -bottom-3 -right-3 w-56 h-72 rounded-2xl -z-10" style="border: 2px solid rgba(232, 93, 58, 0.25);"></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Bio -->
      <div class="md:col-span-2 space-y-5">
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--text-secondary);">
          I studied Electrical and Computer Engineering at UCT, graduating with a final-year aggregate of 80% and all first-class passes. My degree covers electromagnetic engineering, digital signal processing, wireless networks, embedded systems, and more. That foundation is what lets me think about systems from the bottom up, not just the code layer.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--text-secondary);">
          At Cainmani, I've built wind-farm analysis platforms, solar portfolio simulations, a production MS Project dashboard, centralised GIS infrastructure, and the full company server stack from scratch: Traefik, Keycloak SSO, PostgreSQL, CI/CD, the lot.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--text-secondary);">
          On the side, I founded DataFlow to tackle exploitative mobile data pricing in South Africa, and I'm currently building YouCook AI, an AI-powered meal planning platform. When I'm not at a keyboard, I'm probably out on the water. I'm a member of the Western Cape Kayak Angling Club and a keen sea-kayak fisherman.
        </p>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
